Description:
This is one of the main sites of the Great Bird cult: the Altar of Blood. Here, devotees willingly (most of the time) offer their blood to the Great Bird, as it is through blood that the Great Bird binds the fate of all Aquarfall’s creatures. Such is the people’s devotion that this altar is always crowded, with a constant flow of blood to feed the Great Bird’s ambition.

After waiting for your turn, you find yourselves before a statue of the Great Bird, flanked by two crimson crystals, its beak wide open, and nearby, ritual tools for exsanguination and a bucket.

The altar is guarded, and to continue, you must demonstrate your respect for the Great Bird.
DescriptionAction: How will you show your devotion to the Great Bird?
